  "headline": "Sleep Hygiene",
  "description": "Sleep hygiene encompasses habits promoting consistent, quality sleep. Key practices: consistent sleep/wake times, cool dark quiet room, no screens 1hr before bed, avoid caffeine after 2pm, exercise during day, wind-down routine. Poor sleep hygiene = poor sleep = poor health. Adults: 7-9 hours.",
